fulltitle: CIA Covert Operations w/ Fmr. Ambassador Robert White
title: CIA Covert Operations w/ Fmr. Ambassador Robert White
_filename: _CIA Covert Operations w_ Fmr. Ambassador Robert White.mp4
description:
OCTOBER 29, 1996 | Ambassador Robert White criticized CIA covert operations to support brutal, repressive regimes in Latin America while the U.S. emphasized the value of human rights in its foreign policy criticisms of communist countries. He discusses the 1954 coup in Guatemala and human rights there, Contra drug running, and US activities in Afghanistan. He also called for more openness by the agency. After his remarks, he took questions from the audience. 

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
